    "body": "You temporarily need ~9 TB:\r\n- 2.2 TB for the erigon datadir snapshot download\r\n- 5.9 TB for the extracted erigon datadir snapshot\r\n- 0.2 TB for the heimdall datadir snapshot download\r\n- 0.5 TB (or so) for the extracted heimdall datadir\r\n\r\nSo after extraction 6.x TB might be enough for the moment, but keep in mind that the data is steadily growing.",
